  "title": "Brand Marketing Associate [Travelling Opportunities]",
  "description": "<p>We offer an <strong>EXPERIENCE</strong> where you learn skills that will stay with you throughout your life while being surrounded with new friends who celebrates your <strong>ACHIEVEMENTS</strong>.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Businesses that partner with us come in all shapes, sizes and market caps. Your knowledge of people skills combined with your communication skills shapes how new and existing business grow. Using your influencing and relationship-building skills, you become the expert in client services as a <strong>BRAND MARKETING ASSOCIATE.</strong><br>\n<br>\nRequirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Keen in traveling and enjoys meeting new people</li>\n  <li>Ability to set and maintain high standards of professionalism, work ethics and integrity</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Lead marketing campaign in events and roadshows setting</li>\n  <li>Provides excellent customer service while handling clients’ project</li>\n  <li>Help to create clients’ brand awareness and increase sales revenue</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mentorship is key – we hand groomed every single talent here</li>\n  <li>Great environment - positive &amp; empowering team</li>\n  <li>100% performance-based remuneration structure – It’s you who gets to decide</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Travelling opportunities to our regional counterparts – <strong>Get your passport ready</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>IF YOU ARE READY TO VENTURE TO AN ENVIRONMENT WHERE LEARNING MEETS OPPORTUNITIES, CLICK APPLY NOW TO JOIN US.</p>",
